    "text": "calculang is a language for calculations, It aims to be:\n\n• shareable, communicable :speech_balloon: :love_letter:\n• transparent, verifiable :female-detective:\n• understandable, concise :book:\n• flexible, reusable :recycle:\nonly for calculations ⇔ numbers ⇔ workings\ncalculang doesn’t ‘do things’ (“side-effects”) like regular programming languages :boom:\nThis serves to simplify, permitting the aims above for *calculations, numbers,* and their *workings* :white_check_mark:️\n\n<https://calculang.dev/>",
